title: JPEGmini v1.8.26
description:
Put Your PC Through The JPEGmini Photo Diet

With JPEGmini for Windows you can reduce the file size of your photos by up to 5x, while keeping their original quality and JPEG format

Free up disk space
Free up valuable space on your internal and external drives

Keep original quality
Same resolution and quality in a smaller file

Resize & Export Photos
Resize your optimized photos for even greater reduction in file size, using either preset sizes or custom width and height.
